node.text:
This new app @shoreline.app takes nature recordings to the next level and teleports you to another world with immersive 3D soundscapes. Close your eyes, put on headphones, and be immediately transported.
These immersive soundscapes are from Gordon Hempton — Emmy-winning acoustic ecologist — and his audio is unreal. (sound quality is even better in the app)
Each soundscape is a hand-picked location from Gordon and includes a unique story. Our favorites: Bouldered Beach in Hawaii, Campfire Embers in Yosemite, Rolling Thunder over Lake Tahoe.
Get the app for free (link in bio) and let us know what you think.
 If you are interested in being a beta tester and getting a free subscription send them a DM.
